&lt;p&gt;We are seeking candidates with previous experience in auto loan refinancing. In this role as a Senior Loan Advisor you will be handling inbound calls and warm leads (no cold calling!), consulting with and assisting customers in refinancing their auto loans.&lt;/p&gt;
