&lt;li&gt;Effectively manage and maintain a large pipeline of prospective customers, and maintain acceptable levels of conversion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct business in an ethical and professional manner, in congruence with our lender guidelines, finance laws, and internal compliance guidelines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Process finance deals accurately and fairly through financial sources to secure funding&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform needs assessments, overcome objections and manage the expectations of customers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Other duties may be assigned&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hours&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role will primarily work within normal business hours which are currently 7AM - 7PM (MT), Monday through Friday (hours of operation subject to change in the future). In addition, you will be required to work at least one Weekend shift (Saturday or Sunday) every four weeks, during the hours of 8AM to 5PM (MT). In exchange, you will receive a flexible day off to make up for working the weekend shift.&lt;/p&gt;
