&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Caribou is seeking a &lt;strong&gt;Senior Manager, Titling Operations&lt;/strong&gt; to lead the people, processes, and performance of our Titling department as we scale our lending operations. Your focus will be operational execution and people leadership.&lt;/p&gt;
